dc_title_s: Winnebago County, Iowa, 1958, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Image is a photoreduction of the mosaic created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol CAD. Form of individual image numbering: CAD-1V-[number], CAD-2V-[number], CAD-3V-[number], or CAD-4V-[number]."Flying completed 7-25-58" Flown by Park Aerial Surveys, Inc. Louisville, K.Y.
